# Add royalty-free MP3 files here for background music.
# The video_builder will randomly pick one per video.
#
# Recommended sources for royalty-free music:
#   - YouTube Audio Library: https://studio.youtube.com/channel/music
#   - Free Music Archive: https://freemusicarchive.org
#   - Pixabay Music: https://pixabay.com/music/
#
# Naming convention:  <mood>_<bpm>bpm_<title>.mp3
# Examples:
#   upbeat_120bpm_energetic_pop.mp3
#   calm_90bpm_soft_piano.mp3
#   kids_100bpm_playful_tune.mp3    (Channel B)
